{"tid":375541,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】聽講星期六日李氏力場都會放假 Day98 26/8","createTime":"2017-08-26T14:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T17:55:56.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66f18766c95c03cc56618e998fe099823d042110","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=oprbwUJw99tpXiQ1ARWMI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=096365f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=oprbwUJw99tpXiQ1ARWMI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b2f80f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=oprbwUJw99tpXiQ1ARWMI%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0f7faa4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"3d5031e27a61028b4d446d694427a37aacee18c6","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018bacec4e7ad915e43bc1b1448d66ebb14cab98","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d56677e8826c28c6f0a4bab29979bcee590c922","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620ad348a71136b77e18a59ce2857c84d6946a39","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef830ca30304343028fe6996a79373fbc042cfb7","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f85e71e18ab3bd13dbae9e8ba481f919d1d880","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81ac013e7df9074a0df3b2ae42dea599ffcf362","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768793e119aa0fac316048f7458e68b9117b6a37","tid":375541,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=